{"tid":1598954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得如果香港獨立之後，市民應唔應該有持槍權？","createTime":"2019-09-27T17:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T18:10:29.000Z","uid":320339,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1682b0fdc04ba64995e15ac2a4156dafaaaa6346","tid":1598954,"uid":320339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"(第一次開post，唔識排版，請多多見諒)<br />\n<br />\n點解呢個港共政府可以有恃無恐咁利用黑警用唔同嘅武器嚟殘害我哋香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係因爲我哋香港人唔似美國人咁樣有自己嘅持槍權，我哋受獨裁政府壓迫嗰時就冇武器去反抗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，他朝一日香港獨立嘅話，我覺得嗰時民選嘅政府一定要開始教導人民使用槍械嘅基本守則等等嘅事，以及最重要嘅係開放持槍權，等政府唔再係為人民服務嗰時，可以企起身反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇？"},{"pid":"e00ac2da4e6c42b752457e143235cc536d68c497","tid":1598954,"uid":320339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"929 101"},{"pid":"45b3794624accf35ec7c8b6dd3ef36d36016e447","tid":1598954,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"到時再算"},{"pid":"cdcebeebf30e58edbbf22d1f187726cabb68dc11","tid":1598954,"uid":323107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:19:26.000Z","msg":"畀啲冇腦又暴力嘅藍絲拎到上手會唔會命都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bebd24bb987504c8709aef497a40295f55ea8c","tid":1598954,"uid":320339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdcebeebf30e58edbbf22d1f187726cabb68dc11","tid":1598954,"uid":323107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:19:26.000Z","msg":"畀啲冇腦又暴力嘅藍絲拎到上手會唔會命都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"所以一定要做家底調查"},{"pid":"5f45ef356c2c3f